pt.davidafsilva.jtrakt.internal.response

Class ObjectTypeAdapter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gson.TypeAdapter<T>
      • pt.davidafsilva.jtrakt.internal.response.BaseTypeAdapter<T>
        • pt.davidafsilva.jtrakt.internal.response.ObjectTypeAdapter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the object being (de)serialized.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActorTypeAdapter, GenreTypeAdapter, PeopleTypeAdapter, RatingTypeAdapter, TvShowArtTypeAdapter, TvShowEpisodeSummaryTypeAdapter, TvShowEpisodeTypeAdapter, TvShowSeasonTypeAdapter, TvShowTypeAdapter

    abstract class ObjectTypeAdapter<T>
extends BaseTypeAdapter<T>

    The base object deserialization entity. It handles most of the deserialization logic of our object model, delegating only the concrete object fields deserialization.

    Also, it provides a set of much needed functionality to be used by concrete object type adapters, such as auxiliary reader methods.

    Author:
    David Silva
